description.en: DeFi project that provides all features to stake, farm and leverage from the total value locked.  But in addition to the base DeFi use case, the platform will provide 2 unique use cases namely LEAF4FUN and LEAF4FUND.  LEAF4FUN will be providing a plug-and-play gaming platform with an NFT marketplace connecting with world renown characters.  Whereas, LEAF4FUND aims to create Fund tokens to represent investment in real-world Crypto Funds.
